Skills.Name: Bring It On
Skills.Description: Inflicts Provoke on all enemies for 15s. Further lowers ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s. Raises own EVA by {2}% for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Provoke, lowers ATK on all enemies. Raises own EVA

Skills.Name: Absolute Pin
Skills.Description: Inflicts Dark on single enemy with highest ATK for 10s. Further lowers ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Dark, lowers ATK on single enemy

Skills.Name: Idea of the Ideal
Skills.Description: Inflicts Dark on all enemies for 7s. Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies (except self) by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 20s. Recovers own HP by {2}% of ATK.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Dark on all enemies. Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies (except self). Recovers own HP

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Dedicated Sword
Skills.Description: Each time evading attack (CT 3s), raises ATK of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 30s. Further raises DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 30s. Recovers own HP by {2}% of ATK.
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time evading attack, raises ATK and DEF of all allies. Recovers own HP

Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Provoke, lowers ATK on all enemies. Raises own EVA

Skills.Name: Absolute Pin +

Skills.Name: Idea of the Ideal +

Skills.ShortDescription: Each time evading attack, raises ATK and DEF of all allies. Recovers own HP. Inflicts DMG on single enemy
